Some simple demos. 

- wingSet: like the SwingSet Demo in jdk1.2
- explorer: like Windows Explorer but on server side
- frameset: frame support in wings
- ldap: ldap browser


Requirements:
-------------

- jdk1.2 or above
- wings-0.9.8
- jsdk2.2 (tomcat 3.2.1 or above)
- ant 1.3 or above

for the ldap demos:
- jndi (http://java.sun.com/products/jndi)
- ldap provider (http://java.sun.com/products/jndi/serviceproviders.html)


Installation:
-------------

To compile and build the war file, start 

ant all

in this directory.

The war files are in the directory build/deploy. Copy this files to your servlet
containers webapps directory and restart the servlet container.
Every war file contains a index.html, so the URLs for the demos are

http://Your-Server/wingset
http://Your-Server/explorer
http://Your-Server/frameset
http://Your-Server/ldap
